---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Results | Académie Évolution"
  description="Real transformations for men with demanding lives."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative z-20 flex min-h-[50vh] items-end border-0">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 w-full">
      <span class="tag anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.2s">Results</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[.9] mt-4 anim-slide-l" style="--delay:.35s">
        Real transformations.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/65 leading-relaxed mt-6 max-w-2xl anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.5s">
        Before/afters, testimonials, and mini case studies — showing what changes when you have a realistic structure.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mb-10 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
        <p class="tag">Before / After</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-4">Before / After.</h2>
        <p class="text-white/65 mt-3 max-w-2xl">
          We only publish before/afters when the visual quality is strong — otherwise we lean on case studies and testimonials.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl overflow-hidden reveal border border-[var(--accent)]/25" style="--delay:.1s">
          <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[.07] to-transparent flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 p-8">
            <span class="tag">Coming soon</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 px-4 text-center max-w-sm">
              Photo gallery in progress — we publish when a series meets our quality bar.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 border-t border-white/10">
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-lg tracking-tight">Before / After</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-2">When we use them, it’s to show a clear change — not cheap marketing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl overflow-hidden reveal border border-[var(--accent)]/25" style="--delay:.2s">
          <div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[.07] to-transparent flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 p-8">
            <span class="tag">Coming soon</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/70 px-4 text-center max-w-sm">
              Video testimonials — same standard: image and audio quality before we publish.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5 border-t border-white/10">
            <p class="font-display font-semibold text-lg tracking-tight">Video testimonial</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/65 mt-2">The most convincing format when it’s possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mb-10 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
        <p class="tag">Testimonials</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-4">Testimonials.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <blockquote class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">“I’d tried everything and never stuck. With Thomas I finally had a realistic structure I could follow with work and kids.”</blockquote>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/45 mt-4 font-display">Marc · 38 · dad of two</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <blockquote class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">“I wanted to lose weight, but mostly get my energy back. I started feeling solid and more in control again.”</blockquote>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/45 mt-4 font-display">Samuel · 42 · demanding job</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <blockquote class="text-white/80 leading-relaxed">“I loved the simplicity. No BS, no impossible plan — just enough to move forward.”</blockquote>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/45 mt-4 font-display">Julien · 35 · shift work</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative z-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <div class="mb-10 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
        <p class="tag">Mini case studies</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mt-4">Case studies.</h2>
        <p class="text-white/65 mt-3 max-w-2xl">Starting point → what we put in place → outcome.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">Case 01</p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Starting point:</span> Man 40, +12 kg in 3 years, afternoon fatigue, training “when I can” (~2×/week).</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">What we did:</span> Three short sessions (45 min), simple nutrition targets, weekly check-in.</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Outcome:</span> ~8 kg fat lost in 12 weeks, steadier energy, ~90% training adherence.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">Case 02</p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Starting point:</span> Busy dad, frequent travel, frustration after multiple “fresh starts.”</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">What we did:</span> Hotel/home options, volume matched to busy weeks, consistency first.</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Outcome:</span> In 10 weeks, −6 cm waist, better consistency than 2 years training alone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-6 reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <p class="font-display font-semibold tracking-tight text-lg">Case 03</p>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Starting point:</span> Fat loss goal, evening snacking, little meal structure.</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">What we did:</span> Clear protein/meal targets, progressive training 4×/week, adjustments from check-ins.</p>
            <p><span class="text-white/85 font-display font-semibold">Outcome:</span> ~7.5 kg in 14 weeks, habits that lasted past the initial push.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mt-10 reveal" style="--delay:.5s">
        <a href="/en/signin/" class="btn btn-primary">See if we’re a fit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
